{
  "texts": [
    "To better understand the potential threats posed by jailbreak attacks as well as existing jailbreak defenses, we conduct a comprehensive empirical study.",
    "Our study centers on two critical research questions (RQ):• RQ1 (Scope) What are the usage policies set forth by LLM chatbot service providers?",
    "• RQ2 (Motivation) How effective are the existing jailbreak prompts against the commercial LLM chatbots?",
    "To address RQ1, we prudently assemble a collection of LLM chatbot service providers, recognized for their comprehensive and well-articulated usage policies.",
    "We meticulously examine these policies and extract the salient points."
  ]
}